该节点涉及的全局状态如下：
  - stock (read_write): Dict mapping product_id to {name, quantity, reorder_threshold, last_updated}
  - suppliers (read): Dict mapping supplier_id to {name, products, lead_time_days}
  - purchase_orders (read_write): Dict mapping po_id to {supplier_id, items, status, created_at}

请说明你对每个全局变量的理解。它的数据结构是什么？读写操作分别在什么场景下发生？
